Source: cxxtest
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Michael Hanke <michael.hanke@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0)
Standards-Version: 3.6.2

Package: cxxtest
Architecture: all
Depends: perl | python, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: JUnit/CppUnit/xUnit-like unit-test framework for C++
 Its advantages over existing alternatives are that it:
  * Doesn't require RTTI
  * Doesn't require member template functions
  * Doesn't require exception handling
  * Doesn't require any external libraries (including memory management,
    file/console I/O, graphics libraries)
 .
 Homepage: http://cxxtest.sourceforge.net/

